description.2: Someone was bound to stop the madness happening at the Neverland Concentration Camp - Cable gathers a group of mutants who plan on bringing the sham DOWN.
description.4: The secret history of the real people who inspired the creation of the Fantastic Four!
description.5: The crazed conclusion! Spider-Man, Venom, Black Cat, Daredevil, Elektra and the Green Goblin collide in this action-packed, slam-bang finale!
description.6: What impact will Nathan Summers have on the Askani religion?'' '
description.7: A turning point in the PARADISE X saga! What role do the Asgardians play?
description.8: The spotlight shines on the Golden Avenger and the Sorcerer Supreme in the final issue to Marvel Double Shot!
description.9: The Martians have discovered that Killraven is essential to execute their plans.
description.11: Spidey faces off against his newest foe...BOOMERANG!
description.12: Kevin at last finds out who put the hit on his father in prison! But a new danger arises as another cop is captured by the 66 Bridges gang, who all believe he is the TRUE Black Panther!
description.13: Spider-Girl barely survived her last encounter with the Soldiers of the Serpent. Will she survive the next one? Plus, Thunderstrike must be returned to this dimension!
description.14: The real Guy is back! Meanwhile, Venus must face her past before taking down the mysterious creature that has been haunting her.
description.16: The two killing machines Wolverine and The Punisher battle it out in a gruesome slugfest!
description.18: It's "Fight Club" meets Marvel as writer John Arcudi (JLA) and penciler Francisco Ruiz Velasco (Lone Wolf 2100) kick off a new direction for THUNDERBOLTS! No jail breaks; no stolen moneybags with dollar signs on them; no running away to strike another day. This is what happens to super-villains without hope. They take a voyeuristic look at a world of bloody fights in abandoned warehouses, the lure of easy money, and the desperate smell of sweaty losers. If you're trying to do the right thing, do you stay bitter in your lousy day job... or make one last grab for fame -- by busting heads?
description.21: Collects Daredevil (1998) #32-40.  When Matt Murdock's most guarded secret is sold to a tabloid newspaper, Daredevil's secret identity is exposed to the world! How far will the Man Without Fear go to reclaim his life?
description.23: The Universe is reborn, and Genis is at the head of it. The concluding chapter of the first big story!
description.24: Christine and her father are reunited at long last. But will Alex and Dante stick around for the family reunion?
description.25: Date night with M.J. concludes with Spidey being summoned to investigate a new, mysterious villain. How will this stuck-in-the-past mobster handle the new world?
description.26: Cap brings out the big guns to battle Inali. Enter Thor, the God of Thunder!
description.29: The Punisher guns down a bunch of mafia scumbags at a card game-all but one, to be exact. Though this lone survivor is glad just to be alive, the specters of his fallen amicos demand that he avenge their deaths-by killing Frank Castle!
description.30: On'one of the moons of Naboo,'General'Obi-Wan Kenobi'and his troops make a horrifying discovery: the entire population of'Gungan'settlers has been wiped out in a genocidal chemical attack by'a power-mad Separatist commander. Worse,'Anakin'discovers that the'commander's next target is Naboo'itself, the home of his beloved'Padm'! Hopelessly out-numbered by Separatist'forces, the soldiers of the'Republic'have but one hope for success- a hope that seems shattered when General Kenobi is captured in battle! New'worlds, new villains, and new heroes, as the epic saga of the Clone Wars'unfolds!
description.32: Cyclops, Xorn, and Beast set out to neutralize the flaming Glob Herman before he demolishes a busload of human children! Plus, a funeral for a mutant and the fate of Quentin Quire, aka Kid Omega, is revealed.
description.35: Cap's on a vision quest he didn't volunteer for. And waiting for him in the depths of his psyche are his greatest enemies!
description.36: The Abomination has agreed to join Home Base's cause under his own terms. A series of double crosses gets a rogue operative closer to the mysterious DVD that contains the true identity of Mr. Blue.
description.37: Collects Ultimate Spider-Man #1-13.  After the murder of his uncle, Peter finds himself taking on extra-curricular activities...such as bringing down the Kingpin of Crime' as the wall-crawling Spider-Man.
description.39: Collects Ultimate X-Men #13-25.  Featuring many key introductions, including Proteus (the evil son of Professor X), the fan-favorite Gambit and Jean Grey's dark alter-ego, Phoenix. The X-Men are cut to the emotional core as they battle their way through an obstacle course of deadly trials. First, Professor Xavier is forced to confront his past sins when his own son explodes into a destructive force. The question is, will he sacrifice his team to save his son? Then, the X-Men face another internal conflict when Jean Grey turns to the dark side.  To save themselves, and the world, will the X-Men strike down their own teammate?
description.40: Luke and Leia. The heroics of the Skywalker kids are legendary throughout the galaxy. Star Wars Tales #15 spotlights the adventures of the siblings through all manners of high adventure! Follow a young Luke as he becomes lost on Tatooine and must fight his way out of a deadly sandstorm! And witness Leia as she and a strikeforce of gorgeous alien commandoes storm an Imperial stronghold!
description.43: Trey makes his final move into checkmate and Elektra does the same. Who will come out on top? And how will Elektra react to the masked vigilante when he halts her progress? Will she finally discover who it is underneath the mask?
description.49: Shocker and Hydro-Man team-up on Spidey, creating a real fight for the web-slinger!
description.51: What happens to criminals caught in Spider-Man's web? Find out in "The System!"
description.52: When Kevin finds out his father has been injured in prison, he makes it the Black Panther's mission to get his father out of that cell. But who he finds there to greet him is the last person he'd expect to see - T'CHALLA!?
description.53: May's in love with Normie Osborn, but how does he feel about her? The Soldiers of the Serpent -- under the leadership of a powerful mystery man -- are still plotting mayhem.
description.54: Already weakened from battle and with only three minutes before she runs out of air, how will Spider-Girl escape her latest predicament against the Soldiers of the Serpent?
description.55: In the thick of battle, Venus teleports herself and Bad Guy to her cabin, convinced that he is actually Guy Smith! But what if Venus is wrong?
description.57: Wolverine steps away from his present crime-fueled company using guile and wits alone.
description.60: Genis rises from the dead entirely unhinged! Rick Jones awakens from a month-long slumber thanks to Epiphany!
description.61: The Human Torch is up to something. Will he be ready for the consequences?
description.62: Two of comics' hottest characters unite courtesy of Bruce Jones (INCREDIBLE HULK) and Scott Kolins (Flash)! The green goliath and the feral mutant only have six hours to rescue a woman and a boy from two desperate drug dealers!
description.63: What is the secret behind the process that made Captain America?
description.66: Neverland Concentration Camp for Mutants is up and running, ready to experiment on and annihilate mutants. First up - an entire FAMILY of mutants!
description.67: Hawk-Owl has a brand new sidekick, and who better to pick than his own son? Featuring Captain America, Hulk, Thor and more!
description.69: In 1961, the first issue of FANTASTIC FOUR was drawn and written by the brilliant team of Jack Kirby and Stan Lee, and set a new standard for heroic adventure comics. Few people realize that the Fantastic Four -- a family of sci-fi adventurers gifted with amazing powers -- was actually based on the lives of real people. As often is the case, real life was as astonishing as fiction!
description.70: Manga Black Cat and Daredevil assist Spider-Man's rescue of Aunt May!
description.71: Cable stars in a self-contained story -- The Low Budget Action Movie!
description.72: What if Thor and the Asgardian gods fell?
description.73: Mister Fantastic has a difficult conversation with his son, while Scott Lang has a difficult time letting go of his daughter!
description.74: Follow Killraven against his fight among Mint Julep and the Martians. But it's not all hate when a STEAMY romance between Volcana and Killraven starts smoldering.
description.77: Agent X's next hit is Christine Gallagher's father. The catch? Christine's father is invisible!
description.78: All telepathic issue guaranteed to blow your mind! First, it's NEW X-MEN's Emma Frost by David Conway (Vampi) and Keron Grant! Then it's Professor X by Darko Macan (SOLDIER X) and Danijel Zezelj (THE WAGON)! Finally, it's Jean Grey by the Sidekicks team of J. Torres & Takeshi Miyazawa!
description.79: Spider-Man and Captain America take on Doctor Doom AND a suicide bomber who has caused mass destruction at an airport.
description.80: As the'Jedi's top'general'in'the galaxy-wide'Clone Wars,'Mace Windu'must oversee battles on many fronts. But the struggle that concerns him most is that within the'Jedi Order'itself. With the outbreak of hostilities, many Jedi are unwilling to commit themselves to the war, either because of their ambivalence toward the'Republic, or because they have actively joined the Separatists! On a quest to reunite the divided ranks of the Jedi, Mace Windu is forced to confront the same Jedi sword-master whom he had tutored in the legendary'lightsaber'regimen known as'Vaapad!
description.81: Two months after the'Battle of Geonosis, with the forces of the'Republic and the armies of the'Confederacy of Independent Systems'stalled in a series of indecisive battles, the Separatists risk a devastating strike at the heart of the Republic's war machine: they attack the cloning facility on Kamino! Their hope is to permanently destroy the Republic's ability to create new'clones'for'its army. The Republic's defense rests on a'squadronof'Jedi Starfighters'and a battalion of'Jedi-led'clone troopers'within the facility itself!
description.85: Trey's father is tired of his son's incompetence and demands that he fix his problem with Elektra and Melissa by any means necessary. What will Elektra do to protect the ones she loves? And will Murdock reveal his identity as the masked vigilante?
description.87: Glob Herman has learned a new way to use his power: Glob-napalm! With flaming goo raining from above, Quentin Quire faces the newly freed Professor. Who will take the school? Plus, the mystery of Jumbo Carnation's death is revealed!
description.88: BROTHERHOOD PART TWO Mike and Andy are two police officers, each with their own transgressions and shortcomings. But are these sins enough to warrant punishment from Frank Castle?
description.92: Inali Redpath reveals his true nature and his unbelievable powers in a fight with his old friend Steve Rogers.
description.93: Home Base sends its agents to get the Abomination on there side to take down the Hulk. Meanwhile Bruce Banner meets a nice woman whom he quickly takes a liking to -- too bad she is Nadia Blonsky.
description.94: She's a'Princess'with a fiery spirit and a hot temper to match. He's a scoundrel with a'mercenary's sensibility and the heart of a hero. Together they help topple an'Empire'and restore order to'the galaxy. And if they stop fighting long enough, they just might realize that they're in love! Set during the days leading up to'The Empire Strikes Back,'Han Solo'and Princess'Leia'find themselves trapped together on a downed starship, lost in the frozen wastelands of'Hoth'as a storm rages around them. And while the snow flies outside the ship, the sparks fly inside. No matter how hard they fight it, there's more going on between them than just friendship!
description.96: Elektra has had enough of Trey Langstrom and his bullying. In the dead of night she will retaliate. But what will the consequences of this bold action be? And just who is the other person dressed in black jumping around the rooftops?

0.text: LEGACY CONCLUSION Viable options for our heroes are wearing thin. Armed with a megaton of nuclear weaponry, one Exile is willing to make a great sacrifice. In the end, one shall fall.

1.text: Adversaries for years, the Falcon and Henry Gyrich are on the verge of fighting it out! What role will the sinister Scarecrow play in the unfolding drama?

3.text: In the year 2026, a young man named DJ comes across an old hammer with a strange inscription on it. Is this Mjolnir, the weapon of the mighty Thor?

10.text: Manhunt Part 1 (of 5).  The Chinese Embassy in Washington has been the victim of a terrorist attack and the man believed to be responsible is...Tony Stark?!

17.text: Sage and Bishop have been taken into police custody. Why? And does it have anything to do with the murder in Alaska?

19.text: Tila, Latch and Lady Yune continue their exploration into the distant future of Eden’s Trail.

21.text: A down-on-his-luck FBI agent has sold the hero's most guarded secret to a tabloid newspaper, exposing Daredevil's identity to the entire world. How far will the Man Without Fear go to reclaim his life?

22.text: Super hero-turned-private eye Jessica Jones travels to upstate New York to investigate the disappearance of a teenage girl rumored to be a mutant! Plus: A date with Ant-Man? Collecting ALIAS #11 - #15!

27.text:
Hailing from the unimaginable era the 31st century, Korvac the Machine Man flees through the timestream, pursued by the futuristic defenders the Guardians of the Galaxy. Establishing a secret presence on present-day Earth in the persona of the mysterious unassuming Michael, Korvac contemplates the elements of a universe he thirsts to command. Yet despite the subtlety of his machinations, the mighty Avengers discover his cosmos-conquering scheme, drawing the two titanic forces into inevitable conflict.
Collecting AVENGERS (Vol.1) #167, 168, 170-177.

28.text: LOWLIFE PART 2 DD is taking the legs out from under The Owl's criminal enterprise, but that doesn't mean there won't be casualties for the good guys!

31.text: VENOM PART 3 Spidey's new suit has given him a host of new powers and abilities. But with all the good the suit has brought comes something terrible. Will Peter be able to control the dark madness within or will he be consumed by the symbiote?

32.text: Cyclops, Xorn, and Beast set out to neutralize the flaming Glob Herman before he demolishes a busload of human children! Plus, a funeral for a mutant and the fate of Quentin Quire, aka Kid Omega, is revealed.

Cyclops, Xorn, and Beast set out to neutralize the flaming Glob Herman before he demolishes a busload of human children! Plus, a funeral for a mutant and the fate of Quentin Quire, aka Kid Omega, is revealed.

34.text: LOWLIFE PART 1 Kingpin is out, The Owl is in. Daredevil must take this new criminal empire down!

37.text: This deluxe hardcover reprints the material from Ultimate Spider-Man Vol. 1: Power and Responsibility and Ultimate Spider-Man Vol. 2: Learning Curve plus bonus material. After the murder of his uncle, Peter finds himself  taking on extra-curricular activities...such as bringing down the Kingpin of Crime' as the wall-crawling Spider-Man.

38.text:
Spider-Man. Dr. Strange. Adam Warlock. Pip the Troll. Captain Marvel. What threat could be dire enough to bring these heroes together? Only the most feared villain in the entire cosmos: Thanos. For the vengeful Eternal seeks not only the death of his enemies, he seeks the death of life itself and the annihilation of the entire universe. INFINITY ABYSS follows in the legendary tradition of Jim Starlin's acclaimed INFINITY trilogy of cosmic epics.
Collecting the critically-acclaimed six-issue limited series!

41.text: While Mastermind and Multiple Man pull a daring heist in the Louvre, Magneto heads to space to destroy a Stark satellite capable of detecting mutants all over the globe!

42.text: Desperate times call for desperate measures. This means Magneto and Professor X begin peace negotiations!

43.text: Trey makes his final move into checkmate and Elektra does the same. Who will come out on top? And how will Elektra react to the masked vigilante when he halts her progress? Will she finally discover who it is underneath the mask?

Trey makes his final move into checkmate and Elektra does the same. Who will come out on top? And how will Elektra react to the masked vigilante when he halts her progress? Will she finally discover who it is underneath the mask?

45.text: VENOM PART 2 Discover the secret of the ooze! Plus, the debut of Peter's Ultimate Symbiote suit!

46.text: The capital cities of every nation on Earth have mysteriously vanished, throwing the planet into anarchy. In this time of extraordinary crisis, the nations of the world turn to the only organization capable of leading them through this time of strife and restoring political, economic and social order; the Avengers. They can defeat any super-villain, but can they govern the entire world? Collecting AVENGERS (Vol. 3) 57-62, and Bill Morrison's Avenger's story from MARVEL DOUBLE-SHOT #2.

47.text:
One of the X-Men, Jean Grey, has unwittingly attained power beyond imagination.  As the Dark Phoenix, she is capable of incinerating a world with a shrug, or destroying a galaxy with a smile. Can her teammates crush Jean's alter ego without killing her?
Collecting Uncanny X-Men #129-137.

48.text: On a visit to a planet about to be enslaved by the Empire, Princess Leia comes to the fateful conclusion that impassioned speeches and diplomatic missions may not be enough. Sometimes, in order to prevent the death of innocents, one must pick up a weapon and fight, and kill, if necessary, those who would use force to exert their will over the helpless. A crucial moment in the life of everybody's favorite Star Wars heroine, and one that very nearly ends the Rebellion before it has even begun!

50.text: Multiple Sentinels are attacking the student union! It's up to Kitty and her two mutant classmates to save the University and protect the students.

58.text: As Storm collapses from unknown causes, Bishop and Sage respond to a mysterious police call.

59.text: Tila discovers the cost of immortality as she and Latch grow closer. The last of his eternal race, (and from a distant future), the young man is determined to end an eternity of loss…by any means necessary.

64.text: LEGACY PART TWO The Exiles initiate their plan of action to take on the Vi-Locks. Step one: infiltrate Mainframe!

65.text: In Eastern Europe, Thor and the Asgardians seek justice - but they may bring war instead, at least if Doctor Doom has his way! Iron Man and Captain America must salvage what they can from a standoff that could shatter the Avengers with a thunder god's hammer!

68.text: Standoff Part 1 (of 3)  In war-torn Slovakia, a group of troubled citizens pray to the Thunder God for help and he provides it in the form of a divine task force. The Pentagon doesn't take too kindly to this and sends Iron Man to stop the Odinson!

76.text: The Hand wants their "property" back- but are they up to the task of claiming it? Perfect Death and Betrayer are well armed and waiting for them.

82.text: Rising from the ashes of X-Force comes the X-Statix, Americaís favorite mutant team! And the only threat to their runaway success is the rival group of flashy new mutants picked by the public! With the world watching, can the X-Statix reclaim their rightful place in the spotlight? Collecting X-STATIX #1- #5!

83.text: The X-Men are in hiding somewhere in New York when Magneto storms the Triskelion. Will they reveal themselves or allow Magneto's full frontal assault to continue?

84.text: Drake encourages Elektra to recall her early training with Stick. The Hand becomes ever more vigilant in tracking down what once was theirs. A glimpse into Drake’s death-defying past!

85.text: Trey's father is tired of his son's incompetence and demands that he fix his problem with Elektra and Melissa by any means necessary. What will Elektra do to protect the ones she loves? And will Murdock reveal his identity as the masked vigilante?

Trey's father is tired of his son's incompetence and demands that he fix his problem with Elektra and Melissa by any means necessary. What will Elektra do to protect the ones she loves? And will Murdock reveal his identity as the masked vigilante?

86.text: VENOM PART 1 Peter Parker reunites with his childhood friend Eddie Brock. Brock and Peter have much to catch up on, including what Eddie refers to as their inheritance, a strange black goo that will change everything!

87.text: Glob Herman has learned a new way to use his power: Glob-napalm! With flaming goo raining from above, Quentin Quire faces the newly freed Professor. Who will take the school? Plus, the mystery of Jumbo Carnation's death is revealed!

Glob Herman has learned a new way to use his power: Glob-napalm! With flaming goo raining from above, Quentin Quire faces the newly freed Professor. Who will take the school? Plus, the mystery of Jumbo Carnation's death is revealed!

89.text: The reality-hopping Exiles run into the team known as Weapon X, Mimic faces off against Namor, and Morph is forced to host his own TV show! Collecting EXILES #12 - #19!

90.text: Jack of Hearts and Ant-Man, two quarrelsome recruits caught in their own crises! One faces his father's secrets, the other his daughter's fate!

91.text: Below the murky surface of the North Atlantic, Iron Man races against the clock to defuse a nuclear device before millions of innocent people lose their lives. Merry Christmas Tony.

95.text: Volume III collects two storylines: "Trial of the Century" and "Lowlife."   In "Trial of the Century,"  Matt Murdock (Daredevil) defends another costumed hero in court.  In "Lowlife", Daredevil finds a new love interest as a villain returns with a vengance.

96.text: Elektra has had enough of Trey Langstrom and his bullying. In the dead of night she will retaliate. But what will the consequences of this bold action be? And just who is the other person dressed in black jumping around the rooftops?

Elektra has had enough of Trey Langstrom and his bullying. In the dead of night she will retaliate. But what will the consequences of this bold action be? And just who is the other person dressed in black jumping around the rooftops?

98.text: Travel back to the start of the schism between Charles Xavier and Erik Lensherr, the mutants known as Magneto and Professor X. Also, learn about the incident that crippled Xavier!

99.text: Magneto declares war on humanity and the X-Men are nowhere to be found! Is it possible that the team of world-saving mutants have switched sides?
